sql:
SELECT AVG(age) AS AverageAge
FROM employees
WHERE performance_rating > (SELECT AVG(performance_rating) FROM employees);

external_knowledge:
'Hoisted the bachelor’s degree flag' refers to employees with a 'Bachelors' education level;
'Steer the ship of software development' means employees with the job title 'Software Developer';
'Land of the True North' is a metaphor for Canada.
